snippet.title: Long Division trick - Fast calculation!
snippet.description:
Do long division fast using Vedic Math.
Learn to calculate long division as quickly as a calculator, without needing the guesswork often assosiated with standard long division.
This video is the first of four videos looking at this ingenious method. To support free math by tecmath onPatreon (thankyou): https://www.patreon.com/tecmath To donate to the tecmath channel:  https://paypal.me/tecmath?locale.x=en_AU
